	   <tr><td colspan=2>Look man.  I am a 29 cleric, and yes, we are poor a lot of the time, clerics are in high demand in groups.  High end groups cannot survive without them.  Plus we are the only class that can REZ and you get EXP BACK...and you all know how friggin hard it is to get exp back at high levels.  Plus I make plat off of heals in tough zones (Frontier Mountains, Rathe Mountains, ect)  So reconsider your opinion.  If you do not like a cleric cuz he is poor, you have two things to do.<br><br>1)  Get used to it.<br>2)  Play another class.<br><br>Teeil Healrawker<br>29th Season Cleric, Luclin Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
